sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant U as User
    participant FE as Frontend Wallet
    participant LS as Browser localStorage
    participant BE as HTTP Proxy
    participant TX as Tx Service
    participant BC as Blockchain

    Note over FE,BE: Startup and wallet
    FE ->> BE: request miner id
    BE -->> FE: miner id public key
    FE ->> LS: load wallet
    alt wallet missing
        FE ->> LS: generate ed25519 keypair and store keys
    end

    Note over U,FE: Phase 1 Commit
    U ->> FE: input domain and ttl
    FE ->> FE: generate random salt
    FE ->> FE: compute commitment hash from domain and salt
    FE ->> FE: build NameNew transaction with inputs and outputs
    FE ->> FE: hash canonical tx (type/from/amount/payload/inputs/outputs) and sign with private key
    FE ->> BE: submit transaction and signature
    BE ->> TX: validate transaction
    TX ->> BC: broadcast transaction
    BE -->> FE: commit accepted
    FE ->> LS: store pending domain with salt and tx id

    Note over U,FE: Phase 2 Reveal
    U ->> FE: input ip and ttl
    FE ->> FE: build NameFirstUpdate transaction with inputs and outputs
    FE ->> FE: hash canonical tx (type/from/amount/payload/inputs/outputs) and sign with private key
    FE ->> BE: submit transaction and signature
    BE ->> TX: verify commitment and domain availability
    TX ->> BC: broadcast and confirm
    FE ->> BE: refresh dns state
    FE -->> U: domain registered and active
